J5G3 - Javascript Game Engine

Tasks:

rake - Will build  to 'build/j5g3.js'
rake minify - Will build and minify to 'build/j5g3-min.js'. Requires java command line utility.
rake lint - Will run jslint on source files. Requires a js interpreter (js).
rake syntax - Will do a syntax check. Requires a js interpreter(js).
rake test - Will execute tests in test folder

Dependencies:

Rake - To build the library.

Optional:

A command line JS interpreter like Rhino( sudo apt-get rhino ) for lint and syntax check.
Java for YUI Compressor

